@startuml
actor Penjual
actor Administrator
boundary View
control ShopController
entity ShopModel
database Database

Penjual -> View: Buka Halaman Buka Toko
Penjual -> View: Submit Form Pendaftaran
View -> ShopController: POST /shop/register
ShopController -> ShopModel: registerShop(data, status='pending')
ShopModel -> Database: INSERT shops
Database --> ShopModel: OK
ShopModel --> ShopController: Shop object
ShopController --> View: Tampilkan Pesan Sukses Menunggu Validasi

== Proses Validasi Admin ==
Administrator -> View: Buka Halaman Validasi Toko
View -> ShopController: GET /admin/shops/pending
ShopController -> ShopModel: getPendingShops()
ShopModel --> ShopController: collection
ShopController --> View: Tampilkan Daftar

Administrator -> View: Klik Setujui/Tolak
View -> ShopController: POST /admin/shops/{id}/validate
alt Validasi Sukses?
    ShopController -> ShopModel: validateStatus(status='aktif')
    ShopModel -> Database: UPDATE shops
    ShopController -> ShopController: Kirim Email Diterima
else Ditolak
    ShopController -> ShopModel: validateStatus(status='ditolak')
    ShopModel -> Database: UPDATE shops
    ShopController -> ShopController: Kirim Email Ditolak
end
@enduml